    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo describes version 1 of RSVP, a resource reservation setup protocol designed for an integrated services Internet.  RSVP provides receiver-initiated setup of resource reservations for multicast or unicast data flows, with good scaling and robustness properties. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
